# ==========================================================================
#  Prompt Studio — .gitignore
#  Publish ONLY the app source. Never commit personal data, user content,
#  downloaded models, the ComfyUI runtime, or build artifacts.
# ==========================================================================

# --- Personal / user data (NEVER publish) ---
app/characters.json
app/presets.json
app/jobs_state.json
**/characters.json
**/presets.json
**/jobs_state.json
**/GUIDA_*.md
**/ale.json

# --- User-generated media & inputs ---
output/
input/
**/output/
**/input/

# --- Models, weights, LoRAs, engines (downloaded by the installer) ---
models/
**/models/
*.safetensors
*.gguf
*.ckpt
*.pth
*.bin
*.onnx

# --- Binary distribution artifacts (built, not source; ship via Releases) ---
*.zip
*.7z
bootstrap.zip
app.zip
*.exe
*.dll

# --- ComfyUI runtime / Python embed ---
ComfyUI/
python_embeded/
minipython/
llamacpp/

# --- Python caches ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyc

# --- Logs & temp ---
*.log
*.part
*.tmp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
